text: This is the BBC. This podcast is supported by advertising outside the UK. This Leicester Dolok-Giwingsachy for BBC Radio Nengale. This is Leicester Dolok-Gyuncechy from BBC Radio Nongale. Now, Leicester Dollygge, Leigh, Leigh, Leigh, This Leicester, Mille. This letter 107, Nugus in a hun. in Maccillain. This letter 1,001 in 2000, Nugus in Hain. If I should I recall that Courses or Tachartus in a soul more astig, Collishtia in the Gaelic on the Nielan Skihan. He two handson, that I'll be able to the loch in the Durekaan. The law of the law retove RAD Moore Leitja, the E. Ockokok O'Kooke Hain, to chawm in Rage Vick, the Tawrude, and Tockevick. There, I'm, that I'm, be Olinich, and Luch-Cupch in Toilvood a snar, awn-in-Loch. And, if, the Upprach in Tauilvov, a snar, out of the loch, and, that was a black of lear, a starry, how'd I was a vena hulac on in a mann. But, do you have the term, a kielock, the law nondurichan? The other way or nother now a couple of ma'amach to be a keelachog, the Lach of Dimness or Dark Shades or Lach of Gloom. Stochae that's quite, but on the sleigh to heen has a peckon to call the Lach of the Spirits. Be couldch and oomiachachan like loch nigh, nor ureachan. And has antenham a doll leashawn skiel. Have me the doll of eing, Gauze, M.E.M. Donaldson, Mary Ethel M. Donaldson, and Skiall, and M. G. R.E.M.E.N. A. A. G. R. Wondering in the Western Highlands and islands. Chaheigh, O'Hugh, O'Hawr, O'Hawr, O'Hawr, O'Hawr, a wachshk, to furrach in the loch. And it's a-ean that one a cretion in the Leitch de Cretter of one year one. The other Giengein more a-o-o-e, with the sound of Dunya. It is it that the Rowe in the Saas, lechate bline-roa, on the Urp Echuska L the chanagduner-reux, was the bacholica rebo, with ming ata. A veraccae there was a deanu Luracan Cusha in the Cumbug Bachtilfianna. When it had a-h-us-a-lachachic, there was, as a laelea on the Chahuska-I-Lockock, we're a law-feely on in the skier. Chah de chas-oher in the school, and he had a slug-gmour, that he could have known the durachan of at is Farsing. There was one of the caustan to be the taring with each. There's a few grammichan in the Gaul Couchach, barack, if you in the Gaul Agin, a cilock. There's da vat a veckach, it was in the Coor-Ewock on the loch and there was Leyen on the Hineg Ety. Grugeth the Lien for Chown to Kyaun to Kyaun in Lough. and there a line on the heine of itter. Grewgat the line for one or cawain to the loch. He is a glackaggaggge with ruttikin on the ground, shewarn, or clach, or ruttigin in Chorce. Lish not rowe in the commas of the dunya in the line a haring to liang to liug of the commas of the Dunya in Lyon at Haring, Tullig, there are the people as smirnuching that the Chahuska in the Sasson, hithead, and the Chickle orah. Gathe the Chahuska in a vaughan. When there was an opur shakad, he had aught on the, but da yetas. Then, the Rowe in the Douder M.E.M. Donaldson in Vech, in the Wachan, and no one crater of the Choirsah in the Lch of the Durachen. Charrot, there is a verck, gendeeleach o'erah in chishka a glachig, but, gendroa hast, peal, on in the loch.
